The Demo
~~~~~~~~

This Demoversion includes some Levels of the first and of the third
World (Nature and Computerworld). In the fullversion there are 5
Worlds and 25 Levels. And on of the very best features of Danger Dogg
is the LEVEL EDITOR! Great! 

Controling
~~~~~~~~~

Control Doggy with the Joystick (in the fullversion a mouse is
needed if you want to use the great LEVEL EDITOR!).

Doggy moves in the direction of the joystick (walks left/right, jumps,
sit on the floor). If you press the Firebutton and walk in a direction
you can walk faster (or jump higher).

If you see one of this phantastic Digi-Pics you must press Fire
if you want to continue. If you want to skip the Intro hold Fire
after the page with the features.

Whenever a new level is loaded a pic appears. Wait for the "Let`s go"
instruction and press fire to start the level.

