power to make softer scrolling and animations.

What must I do?
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

If you want complete a level you must move Doggy over all objects he
must give the colours back. If you do well, the level ends and the
next level will be load.

There are lots of baddies, Bonus and so on....

